            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1479.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1479.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine&nbsp;the <strong>panko&nbsp;breadcrumbs</strong>&nbsp;with 2 tbsp&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong>&nbsp;and a pinch of&nbsp;<strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;in a small bowl</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>smoked basa fillets</strong> in half&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>smoked basa</strong> to a baking tray and top with the<strong>&nbsp;panko breadcrumbs </strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for <span class=\"text-highlight\">6-8 min</span>, or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1479.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1479.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1479.-step-3-x700.jpg",
