          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1479.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> dill </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Zest half the<span class=\"text-danger\"> [whole]</span> <strong>lemon</strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter!)</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
