            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1479.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of&nbsp;<strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the grated <strong>courgette</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong>&nbsp;<strong>chives</strong> and <strong>garlic </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and cook for 2 min</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>cr&egrave;me fra&icirc;che</strong>, <strong>lemon zest</strong> and the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span>&nbsp;<strong>lemon</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with and pinch of&nbsp;<strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 2 min or until thickened slightly</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1479.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
