            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add&nbsp;the <strong>drained</strong>&nbsp;<strong>pasta</strong>&nbsp;to the sauce and give everything a good mix up &ndash; this is your <strong>creamy courgette pasta</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
